* Assigns gun times to the 5k Race
*
*   When to use:    Just once at the starting gun.
*   How to use:     Update the race name (if different from "5k") and set your
*                   specific gun time in setgunstart.rsm below. That macro writes
*                   the GunStart database field only — it does not update the
*                   GunStart event by itself.
*   Alternative:    Use GunTimePromt.2.O.lst for a dialog box (includes Continue
*                   and field → event copy in one listing).
*
*   setgunstart.rsm lines below — one per race distance, field values only.


setgunstart.rsm 5k 09:02:11.15

* GunTime2Event.rsm — copies GunStart database field into the GunStart event.
*                     setgunstart.rsm above only writes the field; without this
*                     step the event is never updated.
GunTime2Event.rsm
